➜古代男人的啤酒肚是怎样一步步搞大的？
http://www.sohu.com/a/414640465_624188	27699
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/55fffd037a2e48a8b47e7e751b6b0d2a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏天是人类的照妖镜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女子的<strong>游泳圈</strong>和男子的<strong>啤酒肚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一热一脱一个准</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/06bea30b12dc4a06ae06ca3448d0819e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当代男子吃出啤酒肚被叫<strong>油腻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200824/2d1258c951c64227ad88ff735e20e4d7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">古代男子以<strong>啤酒肚为荣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那叫一个潇洒和富态</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还美其名曰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>将军肚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这不</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秦始皇兵马俑们的将军肚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是一个很好的代言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200824/f9b63d58f9d14c579bcff155a983110e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官越大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将军肚越大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么问题来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挺着一个大肚子能冲锋陷阵吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打的是寂寞吧…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/bd9020826d704d3fb740c78b84418e13.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代将军挺着一个将军肚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并不是只有秦朝有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历朝历代都有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可见这个肚子<strong>有过人之处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">究竟是能打还是能吓人呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/451bad57239941cf8eb17df3e33cd21d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>冷兵器时代</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然要打群架</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么装备必须<strong>硬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将军士兵穿上的装备</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那相当于背着一小套健身器材</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>战国时期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吴起带着5万魏军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打败了50万秦军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿下了中国史上以少胜多的着名战役——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>阴晋之战</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时吴起训练出的魏武卒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要披上三层重甲和铁盔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手拿长戈，腰佩利剑，背着五十只弩矢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要能开十二石的弓箭（一百二十市斤为一石）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还要携带3天作战粮草</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
魏之武卒以度取之，衣三属之甲，操十二石之弩
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
，负矢五十，置戈其上，
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
冠胄带剑，赢三日之粮，日中而趋百里。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《荀子·议兵篇》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200824/b1a315eafd254f8fbc39f8e2c10d7e60.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了<strong>宋朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">步兵的盔甲最重有29.8公斤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">弩手的铠甲也有27公斤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>明清年间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说有了绵甲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铠甲重量大大减少了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但少说也有20斤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200824/75ca32c02c6d4aa68e1ecc9a44426b78.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把铁扛身上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这得需要多大的<strong>核心力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搁一个毫无力量的瘦子身上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>早趴下了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还杀什么敌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/743e2799a930465abd23dfb7e6c5972c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时有人会说了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瘦子练出八块腹肌也照样有力量啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时不得不说<strong>“行军”</strong>这回事了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代没飞机火车汽车单车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扛着铁的士兵只能坐<strong>11路车</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将军还能骑马</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一天大概行60里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">短则3天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长则几个月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>兵贵神速</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行军速度当然得越快越好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时肚子不囤点脂肪不囤一身膘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>根本吃不消</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
凡军行在道，十里齐整休息，三十里会乾粮，
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
六十里食宿。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《武经总要·卷五》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/446c1249d6f64f45a7159649b0f792a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是只有坐11路车的士兵需要囤一身膘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（虽然大多数太穷，瘦骨嶙峋）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长期骑马的将军更需要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还需要足够的<strong>腰腹力量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来提供能量和抗打抗造的缓冲力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比起华丽的八块腹肌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肥厚的腰腹才是武将种草的利器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如以鲁智深为首的硬汉们就以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腰阔十围为荣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">久而久之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们的脖子粗得像老虎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越粗身材越魁梧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>后汉班超</strong>就是个<strong>五大三粗</strong>的代表</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200824/f4e63be618124ac28cbe489f300a7c4a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
燕颔虎颈，飞而食肉，此万里侯相也。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《后汉书》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200824/afef17e9f3484137904d05697217b69d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好不容易走到战场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要上阵打群架了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代群架是讲究排兵布阵的格斗战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这么说吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200824/9e03176d6f0944e78ce2e08d9016c313.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在格斗中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">体重越大的将军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果脂肪和肌肉越多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么力量越大越能扛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战斗值蹭蹭蹭往上涨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/24ed93d004554c758fcdb3dbd9c61832.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不信你看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内蒙古摔跤手和日本相扑选手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果肌肉增长不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们就要刻意增肥来增加体重</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">获取降维优势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200824/d3599441ff5b4d35a2305f5c73a7f81a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代没有飞檐走壁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能打的武将都得是五大三粗的勐士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">头大、手大、脚大、膀大、臀大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颈粗、腰粗、腿粗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虎背熊腰成了标配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行军能抗饿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万一打不过还能来一招<strong>泰山压顶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/95c6ac7c75324310a9cf631093b69b77.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>特别说明</strong>的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将军肚并不是只靠脂肪把肚子撑大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是发达的肌肉外面包裹着脂肪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俗称<strong>脂包肌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不然只能算虚胖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试想一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果古代硬汉要保持八块腹肌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不能有一块膘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">必须坚持严格的饮食规律</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无油无盐，少食多餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且肌肉越多，基础代谢越快，越容易饿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">照古代战争那种不眠不休的打法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打着打着就饿死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八块腹肌只是<strong>吃力不讨好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200824/31c4ce3d00144965b49ebfa41fd6798a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脂包肌虽说没有完美线条，观赏值为零</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200824/5a4df3fb1f264efc85a6a30668e0e484.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起码战斗力和续航能力一百分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟当代用奶茶和啤酒喂出来的啤酒肚<strong>完全不一样</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">详情可对照当代的格斗士和相扑选手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200824/fdf97ac0718f4643a0916ddc82ff4707.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200824/0eb5cbf7e5c943eab1a94c61d2619cf0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是说古代将军不喝酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实很多都是酒鬼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">考古学家在<strong>秦朝简牍</strong>中发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了缓解杀戮的恐惧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出兵前士兵将军都会喝酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打胜战也会喝酒庆功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以军队粮草里一般会备很多酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">练得膀大腰圆的武将们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在古代有不少迷妹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说君子如玉的潘安们也有庞大的市场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但丝毫不阻挡将军肚们的魅力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟那时的迷妹们也不崇拜肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且在物质匮乏的年代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>富态和肥壮也是富裕的象征</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
建隆初，（李彝兴）献马三百匹，太祖大喜，
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
亲视攻玉为带，且召使问曰：汝帅腹围几何？
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
使言：彝兴腰腹甚大。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
太祖曰：汝帅真福人也。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
遂遣使以带赐之。
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
——《宋史·夏国传》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/be2870bf56f6428a8fad3f30316b2599.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">究竟什么时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八块腹肌的审美开始取代了五大三粗呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就要问问八块腹肌的鼻祖——<strong>古希腊人</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从古到今</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古希腊人对人体肌肉线条就爱得深沉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>公元前5世纪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">希腊雕塑家<strong>米隆</strong>的<strong>《掷铁饼者》</strong>火到了现在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哲学家也来凑热闹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>柏拉图</strong>大力鼓励体育教育</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奥林匹克运动会办得风生水起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各种肌肉作品应势而生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">画家还联合数学家、解剖医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">研究人体黄金比例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>裸露成了流行趋势</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200824/cc21c159a74f4e16810af21bf1582ba7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相反</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代中国人衣服越穿越厚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捂得严严实实的，还不能光膀子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">画家们的画风也越来越写实了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">武将们的形象都是清一色的“大肚腩”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从汉代韩信到豹子头林冲、吕布关羽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都<strong>大腹便便</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你要说每个武将都是大肚腩们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实也未必</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霍去病偏偏是细腰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保安刺客们也是身材一级棒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但刺客都不是宫廷画家的核心客户</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200824/35490918b15f4824a42180f00fc8a463.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代画师的重任</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是展现朝廷将军的好body</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是他们的精神面貌和盔甲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200824/8ee6860448554803b4e8f06284c85f69.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说白了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是展示朝廷的硬实力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将军要么身穿<strong>重型盔甲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么是一身又贵又厚的官服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便有八块腹肌，藏得严严实实的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又有谁知道呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明代以前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">民间很少老百姓知道将军们的大肚腩画像</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到畅销书插图产业兴起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大量读者爱上看<strong>《三国演义》《杨家将》</strong>等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战争题材书籍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而里面的插图都参考官方武将图</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如300多斤的安禄山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200824/936e7b797d8043599a787e65975212a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样一来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大肚腩画像就上了<strong>民间热搜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百姓不总结不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一总结才知道古代武将清一色<strong>“胖子”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了现代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好莱坞电影里延续了古希腊的肌肉文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>施瓦辛格</strong>、<strong>泰森</strong>收割了大量中国迷妹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八块腹肌的肌肉男审美市场逐渐扩大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">健身房月卡、蛋白粉、营养餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始搜刮各位的钱袋……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伸懒腰不小心露出啤酒肚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也成了着名的<strong>社会性死亡事件之一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200824/afe98ae627724037befafd0f677d529d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
